{"tid":584724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭耀棠：工聯會一直爭取集體談判權　籲政府勿縮","createTime":"2018-03-08T04:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T05:13:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9a87aa0e7a5e0616f18585443d3f89d1a643950e","tid":584724,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180308/s00001/23cef3360c3137f8e47c9c760688c6dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180308%2Fs00001%2F23cef3360c3137f8e47c9c760688c6dd.jpg&h=9e2e6e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴解僱車長風波全城關注。工聯會榮譽會長鄭耀棠昨被問到九巴接連發生勞資爭拗，是否因無立法制訂「集體談判權」，鄭耀棠稱無必然關係，又指工聯會一直爭取「集體談判權」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1997年臨時立法會通過廢除《集體談判權條例》，當時鄭耀棠投「棄權票」。</span>昨天被問到九巴接連發生勞資爭拗是否「昨日所作的因，種下今天的果」，鄭耀棠指兩者沒必然關係，重申當年審議時間不足。<br />\n<br />\n鄭耀棠又稱，工聯會一直爭取成立中央、行業和企業三層談判機制，惟僱主強烈反對，而無論是殖民地政府或特區政府，對「集體談判權」都相當忌諱。他要求政府勿再「縮沙」，僱主也應持開明態度，訂立「集體談判權」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，當年就《集體談判權條例》投下贊成票、現為勞工及福利局長的羅致光昨日表示，本港情況較複雜，不少公司同時有多個工會，各工會存在競爭，對勞資談判不理想，難達共識。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180308/s00001/1520478427192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180308%2Fs00001%2F1520478427192&d=MezgQDZ78dN2uyvmEkEIpZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8644c45d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180308%2Fs00001%2F1520478427192&h=11dff79a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180308/s00001/1520478427192</a>"},{"pid":"505130a8c46fd1900e565420b0a1862526b840a3","tid":584724,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbe866135635711b8784ada71c6e182d57a875d","tid":584724,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f97aab9786dd8d9c34ecf1d7aec3a2a422ba1d6","tid":584724,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/131047_21888938f81cf6ce89893b33d0aa8bde.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F131047_21888938f81cf6ce89893b33d0aa8bde.gif&h=af608cd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14d2f657437a4da8137d087333d013facd291c47","tid":584724,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁無恥都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a5c53c6ebd5cb22e4b02fbfe1ccacbb2d52b93","tid":584724,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}